'''''Mecometopus ion''''' is a species of [[beetle]] in the family [[Cerambycidae]]. It was described by Chevrolat in 1860.<ref>Bezark, Larry G. [http://plant.cdfa.ca.gov/byciddb/bycidview.asp A Photographic Catalog of the Cerambycidae of the World]. Retrieved on 22 May 2012.</ref>

